text: Discover the perfect blend of affordability and luxury in this meticulously maintained home, offering the allure of new construction without the hefty price tag. Step into a versatile den/office space, then immerse yourself in the cozy ambiance of the great room, boasting a gas fireplace and a Chef's Kitchen boasting high-end stainless steel appliances and granite countertops. Bask in the natural light that floods through the ample windows, illuminating the spacious bedrooms, including a primary suite with an ensuite bathroom and walk-in closet. The covered back porch leads to a patio with a pergola and firepit, creating an ideal setting for outdoor gatherings. With $48, 485 worth of upgrades, this home is an oasis of comfort and style.

This compact little bungalow has everything you need. Across the street from the Shrimp Shack with instant access to Hwy. 20. Two little bedrooms (one has no closet), a 3/4 bath, kitchen and small living room. Some updated plumbing. Very handy semi-attached garage has a nice little work shop area. Standing seam metal roof! Use your imagination and DIY skills to update this charmer. This would make a fantastic rental as well! Hurry, you don't see homes this inexpensive on Fidalgo Island very often!

Nestled on the canal with marina, mountain, and golf course vistas, this home boasts stunning landscapes adorned with mature plants and winding walkways, offering a serene oasis. Picture windows frame stunning views from nearly every room, bathing the home with natural light and inviting nature indoors. Enjoy the seamless flow of the open-concept layout, featuring hardwood floors throughout the living, dining, and kitchen areas, perfect for effortless entertaining. Relax by the cozy fireplace in the family room, or step outside onto the spacious deck to soak in the panoramic scenery, creating moments of tranquility and connection with nature. Shelter Bay amenities include marinas, sports courts, 3 par golf course, beach access & a pool!

Experience the perfect one level home at Skyline! This move-in ready 1723+/- sq ft Rambler is beautifully maintained and full of natural light. With 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, Hardy concrete siding, and a 2015 Comp Roof, it offers a 2-car garage, vaulted ceilings, a cozy fireplace, and a spacious open kitchen with an eating bar. The dining area features a slider that opens to the deck, and the main bedroom boasts a bath and a slider to the charming backyard with raised beds. Enjoy the great location with access to Washington Park and all the fantastic Skyline community amenities, including Pickle Ball, a private beach, parks, and cabanas!

The Deception Shores Rural View Lot presents a prime opportunity for prospective homeowners to build their dream home. This 1.32-acre parcel of land has been cleared and is readily available for construction purposes. Notably, the lot has marked corners and the site is equipped with necessary utilities, including gas and electricity, which are available on the street. Soil tests for a 3-bedroom septic design, a lot certificate, topographical survey, and critical areas review, all of which have been satisfactorily completed. The beautifully developed gated community offers panoramic views of the surrounding bay, lake, and mountains. Located across from Pass Lake for fly fishing and just minutes from Deception Pass State Park.

Immerse yourself in the breathtaking beauty of the Pacific Northwest - this gorgeous home offers unparalleled views from most rooms. Enter the elegant living room w/stunning cedar walls & ceilings, gorgeous stone fireplace, multiple sliding glass doors open to the expansive deck, allowing you to fully immerse yourself in awe-inspiring 360 views. Adjacent to the kitchen, an enclosed sunroom provides the perfect spot to contemplate nature's beauty. Lower level w/spacious guest quarters, a hot tub, pool table & fabulous views! Generous corner lot of approx. 1/4 acre, large 2 car garage, attached shop area, RV parking w/hook-ups, convenient for those who love to explore the great outdoors. Don't miss the chance to make this your personal oasis!

This charming single-story residence offers the perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and community living. Step inside to discover a spacious floor plan boasting three bedrooms, two baths and two living areas. The well-appointed kitchen features modern appliances and ample Quartz counter space. Outside, you'll find a large fenced yard, perfect for enjoying the vibrant Pacific Northwest scenery and soaking up the sunshine, extra parking and newer exterior paint. Cedar Ridge is conveniently located near shopping, dining, parks, schools and medical facilities. Also, only minutes from I-5 for commuters. Welcome to your Next Home.

Amazing investment opportunity situated on an expansive 13, 000+ square foot lot with R3 Zoning. This well-cared-for craftsman home offers multiple options for creative ownership. The property offers lovely living spaces including a main-level primary bedroom/bathroom and office, along with a functional floorplan with great ambient light. Timeless details and millwork add to the charm of this classic home. A generous-sized basement awards storage and utility.

Stunning two bedroom, two bathroom condo in the Stonebridge Active Adult Community. This home features numerous updates, including hardwood floors, modern lighting, stylish backsplash's, custom closet organization, new counters, sinks, fixtures, newer appliances, and plantation shutters. With vaulted ceilings and an open concept floor plan, the home feels fresh and spacious. The kitchen offers ample counter space, a new single basin sink, a walk-in pantry, and sleek modern appliances. Spacious bedrooms are enhanced with new closet systems for optimal organization. The HOA covers yard and structure maintenance, a clubhouse, walking trails and RV storage available. Located in a quiet cul-de-sac, close to amenities and medical facilities.

Wonderfully remodeled 2 story home with 77 of Skagit River frontage! Picturesque mountain views across the river, with an abundance of wildlife everywhere. The home has engineered hardwood, quartz countertops, stainless appliances 1 bedroom plus bonus room, 2 bathrooms a huge family room, deck off the master overlooking the river. The 2/3 acre gated and fenced lot is flat, with a carport, firepit and hot tub. This would make a gorgeous vacation home or VRBO! There is also the Cape Horn Community lot which has outdoor BBQ, play sets, picnic tables, and a wonderful sandy beach at the river. Enjoy fly fishing, backpacking, nature watching, or just relaxing.

Beautifully maintained 924 sq. ft. 2 bedroom/1 bath manufactured home in the 55+ park of Lazy Acres. This home has been lovingly cared for and updated and is completely move in ready. The home has a lovely, landscaped side yard and a super practical storage shed. The oversized kitchen is completely open to the large, light filled living room. Enjoy the generous sized master bedroom with built-ins. Many money saving features including tankless water heater, new/young appliances, young double paned windows, mini splits for year round comfort and PVC roof membrane with 20 year warranty! Nestled amidst a serene landscape of lush pasture and towering trees, this charming home offers a unique blend of tranquility and natural beauty. There are multiple outbuildings and most of the property is fenced. Sip on your morning coffee on the covered patio. Inside you will find 3 bedrooms including a spacious primary suite, 2 full baths, kitchen, dining and 2 living areas. Come make this your Next Home.

Discover the epitome of comfort and convenience with main level, great room style living offering stunning views of the Fidalgo Bay waters, Cap Sante, the marina and beyond. Imagine waking up to panoramic views, where every sunrise paints a new masterpiece across the horizon. The downstairs oasis, boasts a spacious family room and an additional suite. Outside, immerse yourself in the tranquility of beautiful landscaping and a lovely stone fire pit, fully fenced yard and just a moment to downtown amenities & the coveted Tommy Thompson Trail. Expenses stay low with the recently installed and paid for solar.
